        {"@value": "無為法", "@language": "ja"}
      ],
      "description": "Dharmas not subject to arising/ceasing. Sarvāstivāda 3 (space + 2 cessations), Yogācāra 6 (+ tathatā etc.), Theravāda 1 (nibbāna only)."
    },

